/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"今時今日去澳門你以為中共冇record?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30c7d26327e202d857c4d605a3006ae2d44c6fe","tid":960140,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"賭馬 OK. <br />\n如果賭場就肯定起到好誇張, <br />\n大陸乜撚都要世界第一 , 起野要快. <br />\n澳門都會受影響."}]}